              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this property to ensure consistent horizontal alignment from both system and custom accessories to your content, even when the accessories vary in size. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The reserved layout width only affects the amount of space for the accessory, and its positioning within that space. It doesnâ€™t affect the size of the accessory. "
